    public interface IGeneObj
extends IGraphLinkableFeature, IFeature, IPersistentObject
    Root interface describing the requirements for geographic objects handled by the different generalisation modules of CartAGen. Other interfaces extend this one, more specific to given types of objects (depending on their geometry type and thematic).The objects handled within CartAGen belong to classes that implement these more specific interfaces.
    Author:
    Cecile Duchene, IGN-F, COGIT Lab.
